# =============================================================================
# CODE REVIEW REQUIREMENTS
# =============================================================================

# All changes require review and approval
# - Contractor changes require client technical lead review
# - Client changes require contractor technical review
# - Business logic changes require client business owner approval

# =============================================================================
# ACCESS CONTROL
# =============================================================================

# Repository Access Levels:
# - Contractor: Full development access (read/write)
# - Client Technical Lead: Full access (read/write)
# - Client Business Owner: Read access + approval rights
# - Other Client Team: Read access only

# =============================================================================
# DEVELOPMENT WORKFLOW
# =============================================================================

# 1. Feature Development
#    - Contractor creates feature branch from main
#    - Development and testing completed
#    - Pull request created with detailed description
#    - Client technical lead reviews and approves
#    - Merge to main branch

# 2. Bug Fixes and Maintenance
#    - Contractor creates hotfix branch
#    - Fix implemented and tested
#    - Pull request with fix description
#    - Client technical lead reviews
#    - Merge to main and deployment

# 3. Emergency Fixes
#    - Contractor implements critical fixes
#    - Immediate deployment if necessary
#    - Post-deployment review and documentation
#    - Client notification of changes

